Señorita, excuse me?

531
00:39:51,430 --> 00:39:53,015
你跟我一起玩游戏吧
Let's play the game together.

532
00:39:54,392 --> 00:39:56,477
为什么？
Well, why should I?

533
00:39:56,560 --> 00:39:57,853
