说唱歌手萨诺斯
He's Thanos, the rapper.

535
00:40:00,189 --> 00:40:02,191
“用我的说唱杀掉一半的人类”
<i>I'm gonna kill half of humanity</i>
<i>With my raps</i>

536
00:40:02,274 --> 00:40:05,569
