Hang on, a girl?
We don't know what the game is.

537
00:40:05,653 --> 00:40:07,905
我萨诺斯大人会保护你
I, Thanos the great, will protect you.

538
00:40:07,988 --> 00:40:10,741
灭霸萨诺斯
Right, Thanos.

539
00:40:10,825 --> 00:40:13,202
