我都会毁掉！
I'm going to destroy
anyone who gets in my way!

542
00:40:20,000 --> 00:40:22,253
你只要在我身边就安全了 你会安全
Just stick with me, and you'll be safe.

543
00:40:22,336 --> 00:40:23,421
好吗？
Okay?

544
00:40:24,672 --> 00:40:27,716
