But I already asked someone to join me.

545
00:40:27,800 --> 00:40:29,760
没问题 是谁？
No problem. Who is it?

546
00:40:36,100 --> 00:40:36,934
你叫什么名字？
What's your name?

547
00:40:37,935 --> 00:40:39,270
我叫敏秀
It's Min-su.

548
00:40:39,353 --> 00:40:41,355
