Okay, then.

600
00:43:42,911 --> 00:43:45,414
Miss 222, you can play <i>Ddakji</i>.

601
00:43:45,497 --> 00:43:46,624
我来打碑石
I'll play Flying Stone.

602
00:43:46,707 --> 00:43:50,794
我们上班那时候
