Oh, your friend was calling you
by your name, so I thought I'd try it.

609
00:44:11,607 --> 00:44:12,858
您介意吗？
Does it bother you?

610
00:44:14,693 --> 00:44:17,237
没有 没关系
No, it's fine.

611
00:44:18,364 --> 00:44:20,824
