678
00:48:17,269 --> 00:48:21,231
你个白痴！为什么踩线？
You idiot!
You stepped over the goddamn line!

679
00:48:21,315 --> 00:48:23,650
- 现在怎么办？混蛋！
- 没时间了！快去捡！
- We don't have time! We've got to go!
- Damn you!

680
00:48:24,651 --> 00:48:26,403
- 快走！
- 一、二！
- Hurry!
- One, two!

681
00:48:26,486 --> 00:48:30,574
- 一、二
- 快！
- One, two!
- Hurry!

682
00:48:42,336 --> 00:48:43,503
- 该死
- 好好弄
- Shit.
- Come on.

683
00:48:43,587 --> 00:48:44,963
- 没关系
- 你看 我们有时间
- It's okay.
- We have time.

684
00:48:45,047 --> 00:48:46,298
冷静 再来
Calm down. Try again.

685
00:48:46,924 --> 00:48:47,966
好
Okay.

686
00:48:50,093 --> 00:48:53,388
拜托
Please.

687
00:48:57,225 --> 00:49:02,064
你这个白痴 因为你 我们全都要死了
Damn you.
You're going to get us all killed.

688
00:49:03,357 --> 00:49:06,234
走吧
Damn it. Come on.

689
00:49:18,372 --> 00:49:19,373
- 该死
- 快
- Shit.
- Come on.

690
00:49:19,456 --> 00:49:22,000
- 快走！
- 快捡起来！
- We've got to go!
- Pick it up quickly!

691
00:49:22,084 --> 00:49:23,043
哎呀 该死
Shit.

692
00:49:24,127 --> 00:49:27,547
- 抓住！
- 快！
- Get it!
- Hurry up!

693
00:49:28,590 --> 00:49:31,718
转陀螺失败 好像会浪费更多时间
With Spinning Top,
it'll take even longer if you mess up.

694
00:49:38,100 --> 00:49:40,811
您真的会转陀螺吗？
Do you really know how to spin a top?

695
00:49:40,894 --> 00:49:43,897
如果您没有自信 可以跟我换…
If you're not confident,
you can switch places with me…

696
00:49:44,690 --> 00:49:48,527
我的位置只有天地神明能决定
Only the gods of heaven and earth
decide where I go.

697
00:49:48,610 --> 00:49:50,737
你们守好你们的位置
You fools can stay where you are.

698
00:49:51,655 --> 00:49:54,157
年纪比我小 说话都不用敬语
Why does this skank
keep talking down to us?

699
00:49:55,325 --> 00:49:57,661
巫师是比我们高级吗？
Does she think shamans
are just allowed to be rude?

700
00:50:02,332 --> 00:50:03,250
快点转
Hurry.

701
00:50:06,378 --> 00:50:08,672
- 好了！
- 成功
- I did it!
- <i>Pass.</i>

702
00:50:12,092 --> 00:50:13,093
打到了
I did it.

703
00:50:14,803 --> 00:50:16,847
- 快点走！
- 也没有踩线
And I didn't step over the line.

704
00:50:16,930 --> 00:50:18,974
你这个白痴…
You goddamn idiot.

705
00:50:19,057 --> 00:50:20,058
成功
<i>Pass.</i>

706
00:50:20,642 --> 00:50:23,353
- 快点走就行了！
- 快！
- Go!
- Come on!

707
00:50:24,354 --> 00:50:26,314
我们快走
Come on, let's go.

708
00:50:26,857 --> 00:50:28,608
- 饶了我们
- 不要！
- Wait.
- No!

709
00:50:28,692 --> 00:50:29,901
- 求你了！
- 不要！
- Please!
- No!

710
00:50:31,903 --> 00:50:33,864
时间到
<i>Your time is up.</i>

711
00:50:51,631 --> 00:50:53,759
宣布淘汰人员
<i>The following players</i>
<i>have been eliminated.</i>

712
00:50:53,842 --> 00:50:57,846
16号、45号、178号、189号
<i>Players 016, 045, 178, 189,</i>

713
00:50:57,929 --> 00:51:03,143
198号、254号、286号、341号
<i>198, 254, 286, 341,</i>

714
00:51:03,226 --> 00:51:06,021
395号、416号
<i>395, and 416.</i>

715
00:51:06,938 --> 00:51:10,525
我们说要离开的！
现在我们都要死了！
We should have left!
We're all going to die now!

716
00:51:10,609 --> 00:51:13,820
因为那些投票选圆圈的人
大家全都要死了！
We're all going to die
because of those who voted to continue!

717
00:51:13,904 --> 00:51:15,822
现在要怎么办？
What are you going to do now?

718
00:51:15,906 --> 00:51:18,575
- 你们自己能成功吗？
- 那些人都是你们害死的
- You think you can survive?
- Look at them!

719
00:51:18,658 --> 00:51:19,576
怎么了？
- What?
- You killed them.

720
00:51:19,659 --> 00:51:21,578
- 都是你们害死的
- 能不能…

721
00:51:20,827 --> 00:51:23,622
Can you…
Can you please give me one of those?

722
00:51:21,661 --> 00:51:23,622
那个 您也给我一点不行吗？

723
00:51:24,247 --> 00:51:25,665
- “那个”？
- 您刚才吃那个
- "Those"?
- The thing you took.

724
00:51:25,749 --> 00:51:28,251
您藏在十字架里的那个东西
You're keeping them inside your cross.

725
00:51:30,045 --> 00:51:32,339
我不知道你在说什么鬼
I don't know
what the fuck you're talking about.

726
00:51:32,422 --> 00:51:35,550
如果我紧张 输了游戏 我们都会死
If I get nervous
and lose the game, we'll all die.

727
00:51:36,635 --> 00:51:39,054
现在我的手很抖
My hands are shaking like crazy.

728
00:51:39,137 --> 00:51:40,931
- 重要公告
- 喂 南秀
<i>- Attention, please.</i>
- Nam-su.

729
00:51:41,014 --> 00:51:42,057
- 各位玩家…
- 是南奎
- <i>Players.</i>
- It's Nam-gyu.

730
00:51:42,140 --> 00:51:46,394
- …清理场地期间 请耐心等待
- 喂 南奎
- Right. Nam-gyu.
- <i>Please wait while we tidy up the venue.</i>

731
00:51:47,395 --> 00:51:48,396
你知道这是什么吗？
Do you know what this is?

732
00:51:48,480 --> 00:51:51,108
摇头丸？氯胺酮？
Ecstasy? Ketamine?

733
00:51:51,858 --> 00:51:56,113
这是新合成的品种 超级疯狂
兄弟 你吃了根本受不了
It's a new kind. It's fucking crazy, man.
You can't handle it.

734
00:51:56,196 --> 00:51:57,322
大哥
Hey.

735
00:52:00,033 --> 00:52:03,703
我在俱乐部做事的时候
基本全都见识过了
I did all kinds of stuff
when I was working at the club.

736
00:52:03,787 --> 00:52:08,583
而且哥来俱乐部的时候
我还往您的房间送过这种东西
I even brought you some
when you came to the club.

737
00:52:14,673 --> 00:52:16,133
你这个瘾君子
You junkie.

738
00:52:23,557 --> 00:52:24,391
看什么？
What?

739
00:52:25,475 --> 00:52:26,601
没什么
Nothing.

740
00:52:28,145 --> 00:52:29,396
你叫什么名字来着？
What's your name again?

741
00:52:30,355 --> 00:52:31,898
我叫敏秀
It's Min-su.

742
00:52:31,982 --> 00:52:32,816
敏秀
Min-su.

743
00:52:33,692 --> 00:52:36,903
敏秀 李舜臣将军说过什么？
Min-su. What's that famous quote
by Admiral Yi Sun-sin?

744
00:52:38,738 --> 00:52:42,242
“幸生则死 必死则生”
"Those seeking life shall croak.
Those seeking death shall live."

745
00:52:42,325 --> 00:52:47,122
所以大家不要害怕 抱着必死的心态
“我死了也没关系”的心态进行游戏
So don't be scared. Just tell yourself
that you don't care if you die.

746
00:52:47,205 --> 00:52:50,333
那么就能一起活下去 赢到钱 走出去
Then we'll survive, win the money,
and get the fuck out.

747
00:52:51,793 --> 00:52:53,879
喂 你自己好好表现吧
Hey, mind your own business.

748
00:52:54,462 --> 00:52:55,547
我？
Me?

749
00:52:55,630 --> 00:52:57,757
对 就是你 你的手倒是别抖啊
Yes, you. Mr. Shaky Hands.

750
00:52:57,841 --> 00:53:01,678
说话态度怎么这么晦气？
所以我就说不该选女的
What's with the attitude?

751
00:53:00,010 --> 00:53:02,596
We shouldn't have picked a girl.
She's got an attitude.

752
00:53:01,761 --> 00:53:04,556
- 晦气
- 真是个白痴

753
00:53:02,679 --> 00:53:06,057
You're a prick
who had to pop a pill for his nerves.

754
00:53:04,639 --> 00:53:06,057
怕到乱吃药的白痴

755
00:53:06,141 --> 00:53:07,058
该死的女人
Fucking bitch.

756
00:53:09,519 --> 00:53:11,438
重要公告
<i>Attention, please.</i>

757
00:53:11,521 --> 00:53:16,693
各位玩家 清理场地期间 请耐心等待
<i>Players, please wait</i>
<i>while we tidy up the venue.</i>

758
00:53:52,479 --> 00:53:53,480
打开
Open it.

759
00:53:56,566 --> 00:53:57,859
这是命令
That's an order.

760
00:54:03,698 --> 00:54:05,784
请救救我
Please don't…

761
00:54:27,514 --> 00:54:30,016
接下来两队 请准备
<i>The next teams, please get ready.</i>

762
00:54:44,322 --> 00:54:45,448
你看着我
Look at me.

763
00:54:47,200 --> 00:54:49,160
我叫贤珠 赵贤珠
I'm Hyun-ju. Cho Hyun-ju.

764
00:54:50,328 --> 00:54:51,371
您叫什么名字？
What's your name?

765
00:54:52,872 --> 00:54:57,627
我叫英美 金英美
It's Young-mi.

766
00:54:55,041 --> 00:54:57,627
Kim Young-mi.

767
00:55:00,672 --> 00:55:05,176
刚才英美跟我说话的时候
我一眼就看出来了
Young-mi, when you spoke to me earlier,
I could tell right away.

768
00:55:05,969 --> 00:55:07,929
您是一个多么勇敢的人
I could tell how brave you are.

769
00:55:09,097 --> 00:55:12,017
所以 英美也要相信自己才行
So you've got to believe in yourself.

770
00:55:13,768 --> 00:55:14,644
能做到吗？
Can you do that?

771
00:55:17,856 --> 00:55:19,190
我尽量
I'll try.

772
00:55:20,400 --> 00:55:25,905
没错 我张金子
经历了朝鲜战争都坚持活了下来
That's right. I, Jang Geum-ja,
survived the Korean War.

773
00:55:25,989 --> 00:55:29,117
这只是孩子们的游戏
我不会死在里面
I will not die playing some kids' games.

774
00:55:30,410 --> 00:55:33,788
我们打起精神 一起加油
Everyone.
Let's pull ourselves together and do this.

775
00:55:34,456 --> 00:55:37,667
我是在朝鲜战争中
幸存下来的张金子的儿子
I'm the son of Ms. Jang Geum-ja,
who survived the Korean War.

776
00:55:38,293 --> 00:55:39,669
朴容植
I'm Park Yong-sik.

777
00:55:42,172 --> 00:55:43,882
阿姨 您叫什么名字？
Ma'am, what's your name?

778
00:55:46,134 --> 00:55:47,052
我叫仙女
I'm Seon-nyeo,

779
00:55:48,553 --> 00:55:49,679
龙宫仙女
shaman of the sea.

780
00:55:55,810 --> 00:55:58,355
我相信我们一定可以的
I believe we can do this.

781
00:55:59,147 --> 00:56:01,941
我们要展示给后面的人看
Let's show everyone else here

782
00:56:03,401 --> 00:56:07,113
这个游戏根本不算什么
that these games are no big deal.

783
00:56:11,159 --> 00:56:15,497
- 三组、四组 准备出发
- 请在天上照顾我…
<i>- Teams three and four, get ready.</i>
- Dear gods of heaven and earth…

784
00:56:17,415 --> 00:56:23,588
天地神明 请在天上
照顾我这副驱壳 天地神明…
Dear gods of heaven and earth,
please guide me through this trial…

785
00:58:48,942 --> 00:58:53,947
